org.framed.orm.model

Interface Relation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModelElement, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RelationImpl

    public interface Relation
extends ModelElement
    A representation of the model object 'Relation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Target
    • Source
    • Bendpoints
    • Source Label
    • Target Label
    • Referenced Relation
    • Referenced Roles
    • Connection Anchor

    See Also:
    OrmPackage.getRelation()
